{"tid":1417319,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"滅火必知「火三角」","createTime":"2019-08-05T16:22:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T16:22:10.000Z","uid":60344,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a524fe4e2e37135c4e1fc342c53fbd29596eb996","tid":1417319,"uid":60344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:22:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%81%AB%E4%B8%89%E8%A7%92?oldformat=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%2581%25AB%25E4%25B8%2589%25E8%25A7%2592%3Foldformat%3Dtrue&d=aRHHWgZm4a4JNL46Iov0BK0J0iXDlbDdnmyxhWT3nOs%3D&h=c3c84ba3\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%81%AB%E4%B8%89%E8%A7%92?oldformat=true</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇人post過比前線消防員睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n「&hellip;&hellip;只有齊備以下三種元素：引火源、可燃物及助燃劑（多數情況下為氧氣），一場火方能成功燃燒，缺一不可。因此只要把任何一種元素移除，這場火就能成功撲滅。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/d/dd/Fire_triangle.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fd%2Fdd%2FFire_triangle.png&h=f08e787b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「當燃料用盡，火便會自行熄滅。當然，亦可以人手或化學方式將燃料與火分隔，使之熄滅。將燃料隔開是滅火的主要方法，於撲滅山林大火時此點尤其重要。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/99/Fire_tetrahedron.svg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F9%2F99%2FFire_tetrahedron.svg&h=d45d4bc9&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}